Africa: Algeria, Libya, Mauritania, Morocco, Niger, Senegal, Somalia, Tunisia

Asia: Afghanistan, Iran, Iraq, Jordan, Oman, Pakistan, Saudi Arabia, Syria, Yemen, United Arab Emirites

Asia/Europe: Turkey

70%-90%

Asia: Bangladesh, Indonesia, Uzbekistan, Turkmenistan

Europe: Albania

50%-70%

That honestly took me 5 minutes, so the spelling may be off for some countries.
